        <updateDate>2020-01-28T19:20:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>FAFSA Translation Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to (1) translate the forms developed under the Free Application for Federal Student Aid into no fewer than 11 foreign languages, and (2) make the translated forms available to applicants in paper and electronic formats.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
